# Messages displayed for comfort levels
chunkcomfort.config.message.1=§6You dreamt of a warm, sheltered house with a comfy fire, a pet, and a carpet on the floor
chunkcomfort.config.message.2=§6As you wake up a thought lingers, surely a sheltered place with a bed, a fire and banners would beat this?
chunkcomfort.config.message.3=§6You dreamt of petting your pet while watching the flames dance within the fireplace
chunkcomfort.config.message.4=§6You feel refreshed, though your residence could use some improvements
chunkcomfort.config.message.5=§6As you wake and look around your house, you feel somewhat established
chunkcomfort.config.message.6=§6You had one of those fleeting dreams about building a library expansion
chunkcomfort.config.message.7=§6Open sky, fresh air... it all sounds so romantic, but nothing beats a place like home
chunkcomfort.config.message.8=§6You dreamt about beating the Ender Dragon and displaying its trophy egg!
chunkcomfort.config.message.9=§6Cats, dogs, parrots!? All in the same place — wild! But also comfy!
chunkcomfort.config.message.10=§6As you open your eyes, there is but one thing you can think of... a parrot called Eagle!
chunkcomfort.config.message.11=§6You dreamt about a world, Dregora... and being sheltered against the probability of being smitten
chunkcomfort.config.message.12=§6You wake and have an existential crisis: how much more comfort makes things comfier?!
chunkcomfort.config.message.13=§6You no longer need to dream — you are living it